---
title: BBQ Pulled Chicken Tacos with Creamy Slaw & Red Onion
description: Dreaming up ways to spice up taco night? Look no further: This mashup version delivers all the flavors of a summer cookout, no grill required. Pulled barbecue chicken is tossed with sautéed red onion and lime juice to form the saucy filling. It’s stuffed into warm tortillas with a creamy, spicy slaw for crunchy contrast. Plus, it’s all ready in just 15 minutes—taco ’bout a dinner winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bbq-pulled-chicken-tacos-779d4910.jpg
